response: Dansbandsdax is a free Dance Radio & Meeting place, open around the clock for anyone who wants to listen to their favorite music, or perhaps just get away from the usual Mainstream music in the regular FM stations. Here you will also find people to talk to, maybe you will find new friends, love or just a moment to get away from everyday life. Welcome to us, into the community!
